00:24:07.586 --> 00:24:08.342
vos?

00:24:11.987 --> 00:24:15.524
a bisl nisht redn, nor a bisl zitsn.

00:24:15.531 --> 00:24:17.617
ir vi- zi- ir zolt nisht zayn mid.

00:24:22.295 --> 00:24:28.309
hot ir ged- gedungen a v- a voynung mit tsvey tsimer mit a kikh un,

00:24:28.367 --> 00:24:31.324
tsvey tsimern, eyns untn un eyns in di hoykh.

00:24:31.396 --> 00:24:32.101
yo,

00:24:32.355 --> 00:24:33.584
un di froy?

00:24:33.584 --> 00:24:35.508
ikh hob ariber genumen zi,

00:24:35.508 --> 00:24:38.039
zi hot shoyn nisht gearbet dortn,

00:24:38.350 --> 00:24:39.491
un ikh hob gearbet.

00:24:39.491 --> 00:24:42.193
aha, un di kinder hobn shtudirt?

00:24:42.403 --> 00:24:44.332
zey zenen gegangen in shul arayn.

00:24:44.051 --> 00:24:49.998
yo, in vos a yor dos iz geven az ir hot ged- gedungen di di voynung? in vos a yor?

00:24:49.463 --> 00:24:52.305
oyf di zelbe gas iber vos ikh hob gedungen.

00:24:52.323 --> 00:24:55.468
in vos a yor? umgefer?

00:24:55.845 --> 00:24:59.045
tsvey, fertsik, eyn un fertsik?

00:24:59.171 --> 00:25:02.322
lozt mikh redn, ikh vel mikh dermanen ales.

00:25:01.548 --> 00:25:02.487
BESEYDER.

00:25:03.810 --> 00:25:09.772
ven ikh hob ariber genumen di froy, dos iz geven shoyn in tsvey un fertsikstn yor.

00:25:09.772 --> 00:25:11.331
yo.

00:25:11.961 --> 00:25:14.126
hob ikh ir ariber genumen,

00:25:14.126 --> 00:25:18.722
un zi iz shoyn geven in shtub, zi iz geven baleboste.

00:25:18.846 --> 00:25:21.388
ikh bin ge- derlebn nisht vayt

00:25:21.411 --> 00:25:23.415
iz geven di koyln-grubn,

00:25:23.415 --> 00:25:25.657
un ikh bin gegangen tsu der arbet,

00:25:25.900 --> 00:25:28.259
un azoy vi s'firt zikh, in der fri,

00:25:28.259 --> 00:25:30.006
bay mitog tsurik gekumen,

00:25:30.006 --> 00:25:33.183
un teyl mol bay nakht gearbet nakht shikht,

00:25:33.409 --> 00:25:36.654
dos iz farshidens. un a un a royber

00:25:36.654 --> 00:25:40.392
hot gearbet oyf nayn hundert meter di tif,

00:25:40.392 --> 00:25:43.022
zeks hundert meter di tif.

00:25:43.180 --> 00:25:44.813
un eyn mol,

00:25:44.813 --> 00:25:47.775
dos ken nor bagrayfn eyner

00:25:47.775 --> 00:25:50.126
vos hot gearbet a mol er veyst.

00:25:50.233 --> 00:25:53.281
iz arayntsugeyn s'geven a bak-oyvn,

00:25:53.355 --> 00:25:55.385
aroystsug- ineveynik

00:25:55.385 --> 00:26:01.196
lign ⟨blakhn⟩ vos m'shit aroys di koyln vos m'hakt zey aroys.

00:26:01.573 --> 00:26:02.495
UNK

00:26:02.839 --> 00:26:06.101
bin, eyn mol bin ikh aroys geganen,

00:26:06.101 --> 00:26:07.924
un mit der ⟨karbit⟩ lomp

00:26:07.924 --> 00:26:10.174
hot men getrogn oyfn harts.

00:26:10.281 --> 00:26:13.295
haynt red ikh nisht, haynt trogt men oyfn kop.

00:26:13.410 --> 00:26:16.040
oyb ir hot gezen shoyn a mol.

00:26:15.120 --> 00:26:16.586
yo, ikh hob gezen, yo.

00:26:16.947 --> 00:26:18.682
vos tsu zukhn gold.

00:26:18.682 --> 00:26:20.417
in ⟨Kongolo⟩ yo.

00:26:20.710 --> 00:26:23.471
ober oykhet in koyln-grubn.

00:26:24.135 --> 00:26:28.601
un oyf a ⟨karbit⟩ lomp, bin aroysgegangen nokh an andere zayt,

00:26:28.742 --> 00:26:32.550
un yener arbetorer hot gegangen oyf an andere zayt aroys.

00:26:32.826 --> 00:26:34.777
kum aroys hintn,

00:26:34.851 --> 00:26:37.224
get mir a gey oys di lomp.

00:26:38.091 --> 00:26:39.840
nor vos iz geven?

00:26:39.897 --> 00:26:42.754
dos iz geven unter a kanal,

00:26:42.754 --> 00:26:46.016
un ikh hob gevust vayl ikh hob gekent dem plats,

00:26:46.275 --> 00:26:48.260
hob ikh gehert dos rinen,

00:26:48.402 --> 00:26:52.710
iz bay yede statsye s'iz azoy geblibn shteyn eyner,

00:26:52.710 --> 00:26:54.262
s'nisht geven tsu ve-

00:26:54.262 --> 00:26:57.863
shrayen tsu got hot gornisht geholfn, shlog.

00:26:58.611 --> 00:27:00.371
geblibn shteyn,

00:27:00.371 --> 00:27:02.435
hob ikh gegebn a geshrey,

00:27:02.526 --> 00:27:04.747
hot er mikh arayngenumen,

00:27:04.905 --> 00:27:07.028
aroyfgenumen in der hoykh,

00:27:07.028 --> 00:27:09.641
er iz geforn arop un nakher aroyf,

00:27:09.748 --> 00:27:11.601
aroyfgenumen in der hoykh,

00:27:11.601 --> 00:27:13.778
un ikh hob es gemoldn di byuro,

00:27:13.778 --> 00:27:16.222
az s'mir aroys gegangen di lomp, ober.

00:27:16.903 --> 00:27:20.452
un mayn froy biz di letste minut hot zi nisht gevust.

00:27:20.452 --> 00:27:21.861
vayl yede froy

00:27:21.861 --> 00:27:24.266
az der man arbet in di koyln-grubn

00:27:24.266 --> 00:27:25.599
klert zi arayn,

00:27:25.599 --> 00:27:28.878
vayl s'do farshidene o- onfaln.

00:27:28.935 --> 00:27:30.889
s'faln arayn di dos,

00:27:30.889 --> 00:27:33.957
s'farshidene zakhn do in di koyln-grubn

00:27:34.167 --> 00:27:36.101
vos zenen geferlekhe.

00:27:36.681 --> 00:27:43.087
UNK eyner geharget gevorn oykhet, dem mayn UNK iz aroyf oyf im ahin.

00:27:43.093 --> 00:27:46.128
a sakh yidn hob gearbet in di koyln-grubn?

00:27:46.128 --> 00:27:49.148
s'hobn gearbet a por, zenen zey tsurik geforn,

00:27:49.148 --> 00:27:53.915
zogn zey, du kenst es mitmakhn? zog ikh, yo, ikh hob nisht keyn breyre.

00:27:53.915 --> 00:27:55.878
ikh hob a froy mit tsvey kinder.

00:27:55.952 --> 00:28:00.907
tsurik geforn hobn zey ge- opgegebn a gris UNK.

00:28:01.082 --> 00:28:04.091
m'hot undz gefirt nokh Doytshland,

00:28:04.211 --> 00:28:05.722
nokh Frankraykh.

00:28:05.797 --> 00:28:07.488
n- nokh nokh nisht, nokh nisht.

00:28:07.562 --> 00:28:10.554
in vifl ir hot, ge- ir hot,

00:28:10.554 --> 00:28:16.263
gut fardint in di az az ir hot gearbet az in di koyln-grubn? m'hot aykh gut batsolt?

00:28:16.584 --> 00:28:18.487
s'geven parnose.

00:28:17.982 --> 00:28:24.155
s'geven, parnose iz, parnose iz geven, dos heyst,

00:28:19.926 --> 00:28:24.155
ven Frankraykh hot nisht gekrign keyn kartofles,

00:28:24.155 --> 00:28:27.049
ho'mir undz gekrign di arbetorers

00:28:27.049 --> 00:28:28.881
gekrign kartofles.

00:28:28.881 --> 00:28:30.729
un eyn mol hot

00:28:30.729 --> 00:28:33.071
bin mayn froy mitgeganen,

00:28:33.111 --> 00:28:36.592
hot ge- zi hot farge- er hot fargesn tsu nemen

00:28:36.592 --> 00:28:39.146
dos tsetl fun di kartofles,

00:28:39.152 --> 00:28:41.747
mayn froy, ober ikh hob ikh hob es gehat,

00:28:41.747 --> 00:28:44.208
un mayn froy iz mitgeganen

00:28:44.248 --> 00:28:48.579
un ikh hob ir gegebn dos tsetl az zi zol arayngeyn.

00:28:48.788 --> 00:28:53.374
zi arayngeganen, zi aroysgekumen hob ikh tsurik genumen di kartofl,

00:28:53.418 --> 00:28:55.135
s'geven a groyse zakh.

00:28:55.148 --> 00:29:02.837
nu, avade. ot dos heyst, s'geven far esn, s'geven genug far esn. far esn.

00:29:01.528 --> 00:29:05.447
yo, yo. s'geven parnose, s'geven genug.

00:29:05.999 --> 00:29:13.221
ikh hob tsugearbet, ikh hob gehat dortn belger, hobn zey badorfn epes fun mayn arbet hob ikh tsugearbet.

00:29:13.277 --> 00:29:21.382
vi azoy hot ir zikh gefilt fizish? gezunt? ir zent geven demolts a gezunter yid? ir geven gez- a gezunter yid? gezunt, shtark?

00:29:17.565 --> 00:29:18.288
vos?

00:29:21.382 --> 00:29:25.323
ge- gekent arbetn? oder s'geven sh- tsu shver?

00:29:23.989 --> 00:29:26.264
ikh bin geven shtark genug.

00:29:26.436 --> 00:29:28.972
mitgemakht dem toytn-marsh.

00:29:28.972 --> 00:29:39.187
eyn moment, m'vet nokh kumen, m'vet nokh m'vet nokh kumen tsu dem. hot ir gearbet, zo- oh hot ir vi, hot ir gearbet in koyln-grubn azoy lang, s'geven parnose.

00:29:37.805 --> 00:29:39.128
yo.

00:29:39.515 --> 00:29:42.999
biz vanen ikh bin bafrayt gevorn durkh di amerikaner,

00:29:42.612 --> 00:29:45.290
neyn. n- m'iz nokh nokh UNK.

00:29:44.259 --> 00:29:46.195
yo, az ir zogt.

00:29:46.195 --> 00:29:48.033
vi azoy zogt men, la- langzam.
